## The situation

Ridgemark Property Services is a multi-trade home services company based in Greenville, SC, serving homeowners across the Greenville and Greer area. They offer four core services: landscaping, yard maintenance, HVAC, and plumbing — the kind of essential home services that homeowners search for on Google every day.

The team had 5+ years of experience and a solid reputation with existing customers. But without a website, they were invisible to anyone who didn't already know them.

## The problems

- **No Google presence**: Homeowners searching "landscaping Greenville SC" or "HVAC repair near me" found competitors — not Ridgemark Property Services
- **No way to showcase work**: Great before-and-after transformations were trapped on social media, not working for them in search results
- **Multi-trade confusion**: Offering landscaping AND HVAC AND plumbing is a strength, but without a website to explain each service clearly, potential customers didn't know the full range
- **Manual inquiries only**: No contact form meant relying on phone calls and social media messages — easy to miss, hard to track

## What we built

### Dedicated service sections

Each of Ridgemark Property Services' four services gets its own section with clear descriptions of what's offered, what to expect, and how to get started. A homeowner searching for landscaping sees landscaping. A homeowner with a plumbing emergency sees plumbing. No confusion.

### Before-and-after gallery

The project gallery showcases real work — transformations that let the results speak for themselves. For a home services company, seeing is believing. Before-and-after photos convert browsers into callers faster than any sales copy.

### FAQ section

12 frequently asked questions addressing the things homeowners actually wonder about:
- "Do you offer free estimates?"
- "What areas do you serve?"
- "Are you licensed and insured?"
- "How quickly can you start?"

Built with FAQ schema markup so these questions can appear directly in Google search results.

### Local SEO fundamentals

Every page is optimized for local search:
- Service + city keywords in titles and descriptions
- LocalBusiness structured data for Google
- Clean, fast-loading pages that rank better
- Mobile-first design for homeowners searching on their phones

### Contact form with instant notifications

When a homeowner fills out the contact form, an email arrives immediately. No missed inquiries, no delayed responses. First to respond usually wins the job.

## The results

- **Professional online presence**: From no website to a clean, credible site in 2 days
- **4 service lines showcased**: Each trade has clear, dedicated information
- **Local search visibility**: Optimized for Greenville and Greer service area keywords
- **Project gallery live**: Before-and-after work visible to every potential customer
- **Instant lead notifications**: Contact form sends alerts the moment someone reaches out

Visit the site: [lookaround-ltd-preview.pages.dev](https://lookaround-ltd-preview.pages.dev)

## Why this matters for your business

If you run a home services business — landscaping, HVAC, plumbing, electrical, cleaning — your next customer is searching Google right now. If you don't have a website, they're finding your competitor instead. A professional site with your services, your work, and a way to contact you turns those searches into jobs.

